Package gg.sep.alyx.plugin.commands

Annotation Type Command

  • @Repeatable(NestedCommand.class)
@Retention(RUNTIME)
@Target(METHOD)
public @interface Command
    Annotation used on AlyxPlugin methods to designate bot command handlers.

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element Description
      java.lang.String name
      Name of the command (eg, a command of "!ping" has a name of "ping").

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element Description
      java.lang.String[] aliases
      Aliases that the command should also respond to.
      boolean guildOnly
      Whether the command can only be executed within the context of a Guild/Server.
      PermissionLevel level
      The minimum permission level required to run this command.
      net.dv8tion.jda.api.Permission[] permissions
      Any of the specified Permission are allowed to execute this command.
      java.lang.String[] roles
      Role names which are allowed to execute this command (for Guild channels).

    • Element Detail

      • name

        java.lang.String name
        Name of the command (eg, a command of "!ping" has a name of "ping").
        Returns:
        Name of the command.

      • aliases

        java.lang.String[] aliases
        Aliases that the command should also respond to. For example, if you want the bot to also respond to "!pong" and "!tennis", you would supply {"pong", "tennis"}
        Returns:
        The aliases the command should also respond to.
        Default:
        {}

      • permissions

        net.dv8tion.jda.api.Permission[] permissions
        Any of the specified Permission are allowed to execute this command.
        Returns:
        Array of the permissions associated with this command. If a user has any of these permissions, they will be allowed to execute the command.
        Default:
        {}

      • roles

        java.lang.String[] roles
        Role names which are allowed to execute this command (for Guild channels).
        Returns:
        Array of role names which are allowed to execute this command.
        Default:
        {}

      • level

        PermissionLevel level
        The minimum permission level required to run this command. Defaults to PermissionLevel.EVERYONE.
        Returns:
        The minimum permission level required to run this command.
        Default:
        gg.sep.alyx.plugin.commands.PermissionLevel.EVERYONE

      • guildOnly

        boolean guildOnly
        Whether the command can only be executed within the context of a Guild/Server. Defaults to false.
        Returns:
        Returns true if the command
        Default:
        false
